erable spots on prey."},{"version":"pearl","text":"It is extremely vicious and will not stop attacking until its foe is incapable of moving."},{"version":"platinum","text":"A smart and sneaky Pok\u00e9mon. A pair may work together to steal eggs by having one lure the parents away."},{"version":"heartgold","text":"Its paws conceal sharp claws. If attacked, it suddenly extends the claws and startles its enemy."},{"version":"soulsilver","text":"Vicious in nature, it drives PIDGEY from their nests and scavenges any leftovers it can find."},{"version":"black","text":"A smart and sneaky Pok\u00e9mon. A pair may work together to steal eggs by having one lure the parents away."},{"version":"white","text":"A smart and sneaky Pok\u00e9mon. A pair may work together to steal eggs by having one lure the parents away."},{"version":"black-2","text":"A smart and sneaky Pok\u00e9mon, it makes its opponents flinch by suddenly showing the claws hidden in its paws."},{"version":"white-2","text":"A smart and sneaky Pok\u00e9mon, it makes its opponents flinch by suddenly showing the claws hidden in its paws."},{"version":"x","text":"It feeds on eggs stolen from nests. Its sharply hooked claws rip vulnerable spots on prey."},{"version":"y","text":"Its paws conceal sharp claws. If attacked, it suddenly extends the claws and startles its enemy."},{"version":"omega-ruby","text":"Sneasel scales trees by punching its hooked claws into the bark. This Pok\u00e9mon seeks out unguarded nests and steals eggs for food while the parents are away."},{"version":"alpha-sapphire","text":"Sneasel scales trees by punching its hooked claws into the bark. This Pok\u00e9mon seeks out unguarded nests and steals eggs for food while the parents are away."},{"version":"sun","text":"It has a cunning yet savage disposition. It waits for parents to leave their nests, and then it sneaks in to steal their eggs."},{"version":"moon","text":"It uses its claws to poke holes in eggs so it can slurp out the insides. Breeders consider it a scourge and will drive it away or eradicate it."},{"version":"ultra-sun","text":"They will cooperate to steal eggs from the nests of bird Pok\u00e9mon, but fights break out to determine which one gets to eat the eggs."},{"version":"ultra-moon","text":"It blends into the dark of night to ambush its prey. Sneasel will attack Sandshrew, but its hard skin can cause Sneasel\u2019s claws to snap off."},{"version":"sword","text":"Its paws conceal sharp claws. If attacked, it suddenly extends the claws and startles its enemy."},{"version":"shield","text":"It has a cunning yet savage disposition. It waits for parents to leave their nests, and then it sneaks in to steal their eggs."},{"version":"legends-arceus","text":"Its sturdy, curved claws are ideal for traversing precipitous cliffs. From the tips of these claws drips a venom that infiltrates the nerves of any prey caught in Sneasel's grasp."}],"evo":{"name":"sneasel","level":0,"min_level":null,"trigger":null,"item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":null,"turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"weavile","level":1,"min_level":null,"trigger":"level-up","item":null,"held_item":"razor-claw","known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":"night","turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[]},{"name":"sneasler","level":1,"min_level":null,"trigger":"level-up","item":null,"held_item":"razor-claw","known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":"day","turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[]}]},"sprite":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/215.png","shiny":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/maste